#!F-adobe-helvetica-medium-r-normal--18*
#!N 
#!CDarkGreen 
#!N  #!Rconpop Control Panel Options Menu #!N #!EC #!N #!N The 
 #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Options #!EF menu allows you to customize the Control Panel. 
#!N #!N The  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Options #!EF menu contains the following options: 
#!N #!I0 #!N #!N #!I0 #!N  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Change Control Panel Name... 
#!EF #!I50 #!N Displays a dialog box where you can enter 
a new name for the current Control Panel. #!N #!I0 #!N 
 #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Control Panel Access... #!EF #!I50 #!N Allows you to specify 
which control panels and control panel groups are accessible from the 
Control Panel's  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Open All Control Panels #!EF option under the 
 #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Windows #!EF menu. See  #!Lrcpa,dxall406 h Restricting Control Panel Access  #!EL  . #!N #!I0 #!N  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   
Grid... #!EF #!I50 #!N Allows you to select the grid type 
you want to use on the layout area. A dialog box 
displays the choices. See  #!Lwindset,dxall353 h Customizing the VPE Window  #!EL  for more information about the  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   
Grid... #!EF option. See  #!Lccpgrid,dxall392 h Changing the Alignment of Interactors in the Control Panel  #!EL  . #!N #!I0 #!N  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Dialog 
Style #!EF #!I50 #!N Changes a control panel to "dialog style" 
(see  #!Lcpadbs,dxall403 h Control Panels as Dialog Boxes  #!EL  ). #!N #!I0 #!N  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Startup Control Panel #!EF 
#!I50 #!N Allows you to specify whether the Control Panel is 
opened automatically when Data Explorer is started with the Image window 
or menu bar as the anchor window. See  #!Lstartcp,dxall407 h Specifying a Startup Control Panel  #!EL  . #!I0 
